Output demos/find-cards.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 100ms
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "export PATH=$PWD/target/release:$PATH" Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "# Find and edit cards with fuzzy search" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "zen find France" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "rust" Sleep 300ms
Sleep 1s

Backspace 4
Sleep 500ms

Type "capital" Sleep 300ms
Sleep 1s

Down
Sleep 500ms

Up
Sleep 500ms

Escape
Sleep 1s
